org.gbif.dwc.text

Class ArchiveFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.dwc.text.ArchiveFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Record>

    public class ArchiveFile
extends Object
implements Iterable<Record>
    This class can be used to encapsulate information about a file contained within a Darwin Core Archive. It generally represents the fileType object described in the Darwin Core Archive XSD.
    See Also:
    Darwin Core Archive XSD
